cohortName: [PL 81931001] Psoriasis with arthropathy referent concept incident cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants with >=365d prior observation
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (81931) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: [PL 81931002] Psoriasis with arthropathy referent concept prevalent cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (81931) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: [PL 81931003] Psoriatic arthritis at first diagnosis from components (excluding dactylitis, mutilans)
logicDescription: Psoriatic arthritis defined by code or components at first diagnosis with 365 days of continous observation. Cohort exist is the end of continous observable time for the person.
